title: Lindsey Buckingham and Stevie Nicks - their album (1973)
description: Lindsey Buckingham & Stevie Nicks' album "Buckingham Nicks" was released in September 1973. They joined Fleetwood Mac around the end of 1974. https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buckingham_Nicks Track listing: 01 Crying In The Night (LP version) 02 Stephanie 03 Without A Leg To Stand On 04 Crystal 05 Long Distance Winner 06 Don't Let Me Down Again 07 Django 08 Races Are Run 09 Lola (My Love) 10 Frozen Love 11 Crying In The Night (45 version) These tracks are from a CD labeled "Anthem Records Collector's Edition". The CD also says "Anthem 5058" and "Made In Australia"
